	<h5><pstyle="color:#f0f0f7">  Instruction for Online Test</p>
<p style="color:red">Please read the Instructions carefully before starting the test.</p><br>
<p style="color:white">
	1. Click start test on bottom of your screen to begin the test.<br>
	2. The clock has been set at sever and count down timer at the top Right side of the screen will display left out time to closure from where you can monitor time you have to complete the exam.<br>
	3. Click one of the answer, simply click the desired option button. <br>
	4. Candidate can change their response of attempted answer anytime during examination slot time by clicking another answer which candidates want to
		change an answer. Click to remove incorrect answer, click the desired option button. <br>
	5. Click on Next to save the answer and moving to the next question. The next question will automatically be displayed.<br>
	6. Click on Mark for Review to review you answer at later stage.<br>
 	7. To select a question, click on the question number on the Right side of the screen.<br>
	8. The colour coded diagram on the Left side of the screen shows the status of the question.<br>
	9.Candidate will be allowed to Shuffle between questions anytime during the examination as per their convenience.<br>
	10. All the answered questions will be counted for calculating the final score.<br>
	11. Do not click final SUBMIT on the left corner of the screen unless you have completed the exam. In case you click final SUBMIT you will not be permitted
		to continue.<br>
	12. Score obtained will be displayed immediately after the test.<br>
</h5>
